\begin_layout Standard
The Match dialog is the central dialog in the data-entry process.
 It allows the user to enter high-level information on the match, such as
 its date, the competition and matchday to which the match belongs, the
 match venue and the central referee, the competing teams and associated
 managers, and the elapsed match time.
 This dialog will open only if the following pre-competition conditions
 have been met:
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize
At least one entry in Competition table
